                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Provides suggestions for raising the numbers necessary for the next
                    national draft. Urges readers, for instance, to form enrollment committees in
                    each township that can compile names of eligible men.</summary>
                <note/>
